Sentencas: Core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (LSCF@GDC) composite materials are synthesized and sintered as the SOFC cathodes by screen-printing method.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: The durability of core-shell-structured LSCF@GDC composite cathodes are evaluated through constant current polarizations (CCP) process at 750 degrees C and the results indicate that the core-shell-structured LSCF@GDC composite cathode (nanorod, 0.6) possesses an excellent long-term stability.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: In addition, molecular dynamics (MD) model is developed and applied to simulate the interaction between LSCF and GDC particles.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: According to the simulation results, compressive stress is generated at the cathode-electrolyte interface by the coated GDC layer.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: Combining with the X-ray diffraction (XRD) refinement results, it's revealed that the lattice strains are introduced in LSCF lattices because of the compressive stress.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: Furthermore, XPS results show that the core-shell-structured LSCF@GDC composite cathode (nanorod, 0.6) possess a better inhibition ability for Sr surface segregation.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes

Sentencas: This study provides a possible way to suppress Sr surface segregation.
Titulo: Study on durability of novel core-shell-structured La0.8Sr0.2Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ@Gd0.2Ce0.8O1.9 composite materials for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes
